Cell["\<\
(Note that the units are still in days: Whether I use a month, a year, or a \
decade of daily closing prices, they are still daily closing prices.)  \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.974436294218916*^9, 3.9744363344133663`*^9}, {
